/**
 * SentinelDaemon - Active Monitoring & Enforcement Daemon
 *
 * Continuously monitors:
 * - File system changes
 * - Agent claims
 * - Code submissions
 *
 * Enforces QoreLogic policies through:
 * - Heuristic pattern matching
 * - Optional LLM-assisted evaluation
