 * MythologIQ: FailSafe (feat. QoreLogic)
 *
 * Main extension entry point that orchestrates:
 * - Genesis: Planning & Visualization Layer
 * - QoreLogic: Governance Content & Framework
 * - Sentinel: Active Monitoring & Enforcement
